<section><aside id="sidebar"></aside><article><%=window.story.render("CenterDialogs")%>
<%window.gm.player.location=window.passage.name;%>
<h2>Your unfortunate journey brought you here</h2> 
<p>...While traveling the wasteland, some bandits surprised your resting carawan.</p>
<p>[[Fight]] | [[Run off into the dark]] | [[Sit it out]]</p>
<p>Now you are following with your hands bound to a place called Zhuul.</p>
<p>After a days walk, a city comes into view. Compared to the deserted wastes you passed through until now, the surrounding of the city seems much more lively.</p>
<p>Without much of a rest, you are lead to a place close outside the walls of the city. And it quickly dawns on you whats going to happen: a slave auction</p>
<p>A middle aged man in some leather armor bought you. </p>
<a0 onclick='window.story.show("ZU_GladiatorIntro")'>You are now owned by him</a>
