:: ZU_GladiatorIntro
<section><aside id="sidebar"></aside><article><%=window.story.render("CenterDialogs")%>
<%window.gm.player.location=window.passage.name;%>
<p>"I'm Thesus, owner of gladiator school. I will give you a chance to fight for your life in our arena."</p>
Comply to his terms and tell him about your skills: none | sword fight | wrestling | throwing | actor
<p>Shows you your place to stay</p>
<p>"You are not allowed to leave my home unless I say so. Maybe if you do well, I will let you walk outside."</p>
<p> Leaving the city is not allowed in general and I would advise against doing so in general. 
The city is an supple oasis compared to its surrounding. A lot of nasty things can occur to someone trying to make his way through the wastes. Let alone a runaway slave." </p>

[[ZU_GoSleep]]
</article><article id="LogPanel"></article></section>

:: ZU_GoSleep
<section><aside id="sidebar"></aside><article><%=window.story.render("CenterDialogs")%>
<p>You lay down on your bunk to rest.</p>

<a0 onclick='sleep()'>Rest a while</a>
</article><article id="LogPanel"></article></section>
<script>function sleep(){
    if(window.story.state.Settings.autoSave) window.gm.toasty.info("auto save"),window.storage.saveBrowser("saveAuto");
    window.gm.forwardTime(700);
    let _b,_s=window.gm.player.Stats.get('satiation').value;
    //more energy if not hungry
    _b=30+(_s>70)?100:((_s>30)?50:20);
    window.gm.player.Stats.increment("energy",_b); //Todo move to wakeup?
    window.gm.player.Stats.increment("will",_b/2);
    window.story.show("ZU_NightDream");
}
</script>

